  "time_ut": 1614676389,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "Singapore Space Challenge \u0dad\u0dbb\u0d9f\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0da2\u0dba\u0d9c\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dab\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka also won the Singapore Space Challenge",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The SEDS_LunarBot team from Sri Lanka managed to be among the top three teams in the Singapore Space Challenge 2021 tournament.",
        "The task given to the teams at this year's Singapore Space Challenge 2021 was to \"design a rover that would be able to perform excavations on the Moon and use local resources.\"",
        "The SEDS_LunarBot team's design managed to be among the 03 best products in this tournament. The SEDS_LunarBot team also won the Distinction Award given to the two best emerging teams and won a cash prize of 1,000 Singapore dollars. The first place in this tournament was won by a New Zealand team made up of experts in the fields related to space exploration.",
        "America, England, United Arab Emirates, Australia, Canada are participating in this international competition organized by Singapore Space Technologies LTD with the support of the American Embassy in Singapore, AWS Educate, Office for Space Technology and Industry - Singapore, Singapore Digital, and Shiseido Japan. , and more than 140 teams participated representing 18 countries, including Belgium. About 600 students between the ages of 15-25 years represented these teams and several teams consisting of university students and the SEDS_LunarBot team representing Sri Lanka also appeared.",
        "The SEDS_LunarBot team consisted of three 18-year-old high school students and a first-year university student. They are Colombo DS. They are Viduranga Landes studying at Senanayake College, Jude Peiris and Oshadha Pathirana studying at St. Benedict's College Colombo and Samitha Ranasinghe studying at Purdue University in the United States of America."
      ],
